|`ctrl+o`| `#` | ordered list |
|`ctrl+k`| | code |
|`alt+t`| `|| ` | table cell |
|`alt+h`| `|!|` | table head |
|`alt+s`| ` ~~ ~~` | ~~strikeout~~ |
|`alt+w` | `<$>` | widget call |
